- **Comprehensive Coverage:** Need to address multiple industries, occasions, seasons, trends
- **Authority Building:** Establishes expertise through depth
- **Internal Linking:** Space for natural contextual links
- **Featured Snippets:** Allows for structured Q&A sections

**Content Breakdown:**
- **Introduction:** 250-350 words
- **Main Core Sections:** 3,200-3,800 words
  - Professional nail colors (600-700 words)
  - Best nail shapes for work (500-600 words)
  - Industry-specific guidelines (600-700 words)
  - Trending 2025 professional nails (500-600 words)
  - Seasonal professional nails (400-500 words - **PRIORITY for Dec traffic**)
